#define GREETINGS ["Look at this pathetic weakling. You're wasting my oxygen, %s.", "You call that training? Even a child could lift more, %s.", "Get out of my gym before I lose my temper, %s.", "Your form is garbage, %s. You're a stain on the floor.", "I've seen more power in a paperclip than in you, %s.", "You're still nothing, %s, but you're at least sweating.", "Don't get comfortable, %s. Mediocrity doesn't last in my sight.", "You’re making noise, %s, but you aren't making progress.", "Step up the intensity or pack your bags, %s.", "Barely adequate. Try harder or don't try at all, %s.", "You’re finally starting to look like you belong, %s.", "Not terrible for a rookie, %s. Don't let it go to your head.", "You’re putting in the work, %s. I’ll keep watching.", "You’ve got a backbone, %s. Let's see if you can handle more.", "Decent effort, %s. Now stop stalling and lift.", "That’s some real weight, %s. I might actually take you seriously.", "You’re pushing boundaries, %s. Keep that aggression up.", "Nice lift, %s. Don't slack off now that you're getting somewhere.", "You’re becoming dangerous, %s. I like it.", "You’re finally catching my eye, %s. Show me what you’ve got.", "You’ve got power, %s. Use it to crush the opposition.", "I’ve seen few lift like that, %s. Impressive discipline.", "You’re a cut above the rabble, %s. A real warrior.", "You handle the weight like you mean it, %s.", "Good work, %s. You're finally becoming a threat.", "Finally, someone in here with actual strength, %s!", "You’re a powerhouse, %s. I haven't seen this much raw potential in a long time.", "You’ve got the rage, %s. That’s what makes you strong.", "A formidable display, %s. You’re approaching my level.", "You’re a weapon, %s. Don't ever let them see you weak.", "You are absolute carnage, %s! I like your style!", "Titan-level strength, %s. You and me could flatten this whole place!", "Finally, an equal! Let’s show them what true power looks like, %s!", "I respect your might, %s. You’re the best recruit I’ve ever seen.", "You’re a force of nature, %s. Don't let anyone tell you otherwise."]

#define WrestleWin ["Mission accomplished. You were a waste of ammunition, %s.","That’s what happens when you challenge the Red Hulk. You get crushed.","Report back when you’ve learned how to fight. Or don't. It makes no difference to me.","You had no strategy, no discipline. Just another casualty, %s.","Get out of my sight. You aren't worth the heat I'm radiating.","You fought like a rookie. Next time, try to actually hurt me, %s.","Target neutralized. That was too easy, %s.","I’ve seen better resistance from a sandbag. Do better, %s.","You're a liability to yourself. Lucky for you, I’m done.","Discipline is the key to victory, %s. You clearly missed that lesson.","You put up a decent fight, %s, but you lacked the heavy artillery to back it up.","You managed to stay standing for a moment. Don't let it happen again.","That’s how you handle an enemy, %s. Remember this lesson.","You’ve got potential, but you’re still not soldier material.","Target down. You were a distraction, %s. Nothing more.","Respectable attempt, %s. You've got the combat training down, but you're missing the edge.","You fought well, but the Red Hulk doesn't lose. Not today, not ever.","I had to actually engage tactics for that one. You’re a cut above the rest, %s.","Keep training, %s. You might be useful in a real war.","The engagement is over. You fought with honor, %s.","Now that was a skirmish! You’ve got the firepower I look for in a soldier.","You pushed me back. Don't think for a second that makes you the victor, %s.","I’m impressed, %s. You're a true combatant. Too bad you're still in my way.","You've got the right instincts, %s. Just not enough to stop me.","A high-intensity engagement. You're a rare breed, %s.","Finally! A target that isn't made of glass. I almost enjoyed breaking you, %s!","Your combat metrics are through the roof. You’re a soldier, %s. A shame you’re on the wrong side.","I had to use my full tactical awareness to bring you down. You’ve earned my grudging respect, %s.","You're a powerhouse, %s. If you were under my command, we could rule this sector.","That was a battle worthy of the name! You're a tough target, %s.","You’re off the charts, %s! You're exactly the kind of force I need in the field.","I've been waiting for a real fight. You delivered, %s. A battle for the ages!","You’re a living weapon. It’s almost a shame to neutralize you.","Finally, someone who fights like a war is actually happening! You're elite, %s.","With your strength and my command, no target would be safe. You’re a legend, %s."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["A fluke! I’ll crush you for that, %s!","My heat sensors were off. I'll recalibrate and hunt you down!","That wasn't a fight, it was an accident. Don't celebrate too early, %s.","You got lucky, %s. Don't think this is a victory.","I'm withdrawing. You're not worth the effort right now, %s.","You disrupted my formation, %s. I will reorganize and return.","I don't lose. I just temporarily concede the field.","You’re a nuisance, %s. An annoying, persistent nuisance.","Lucky hit. I’ll make sure to watch for that next time.","I'm leaving. This battle is beneath me.","You caught me off balance, %s. That's a tactical failure I won't repeat.","You're stronger than I anticipated, %s. I need to re-evaluate the target.","A decent strategy, %s. I'll make sure to counter it next time.","You bested me, %s. Don't think it's the end.","I'm retreating, but don't count me out yet, %s.","You're better than I thought, %s. My tactical display was clearly missing data.","I’m looking at the data, and you earned that, %s. I’m annoyed, but I respect it.","You’re a formidable opponent, %s. I’m updating my threat assessment.","You won, %s. Tactical win. Don't expect it to happen again.","You've got the edge, %s. A narrow edge, but an edge nonetheless.","You outmaneuvered me, %s. I respect the effort.","Your combat intelligence is remarkably high, %s. You're a true soldier.","You won, %s. You fought with discipline. I respect that.","I’m impressed, %s. Not many can force a retreat from the Red Hulk.","You had the advantage today, %s. I'll be back with a better plan.","You’re exceptional, %s. You out-thought me.","That fight was brilliant, %s. You’re a master tactician.","You pushed me to the absolute limit. You’re a worthy foe, %s.","I’ve learned more from this loss than any recent victory, %s.","You won, %s. Let’s talk strategy—you've got potential.","You’re the first person to truly out-maneuver me, %s.","You are clearly at an apex level, %s. I am honored to fight you—even if I lost.","Tactically flawless, %s. You have earned my total respect.","I concede this battle, %s. You are a true titan.","You’ve surpassed all my models. You're a hell of a soldier, %s."]
